## **ðŸŽ¯ Key Benefits of This Approach**
âœ… **No Temporary Files**: Everything is done **in-memory using streams**.  
âœ… **Efficient**: Reduces I/O operations and saves disk space.  
âœ… **End-to-End Secure Processing**: Files are encrypted and uploaded directly.  
âœ… **Works for Large Files**: The **streaming approach avoids memory overflow**.

